<body>

    <!-- Main Shloka Section -->
    <div class="shloka-container">
        <h1>📜 Bhagavad Geeta Shlokas</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Self-Discipline & Control (Mind Mastery) – Control desires and emotions; they should not control you.</p>
        <!-- Wrapper Box for All Shlokas -->
        <br />
        <div class="shloka-wrapper">
            <h2>Adhyay 1 Shloka</h2>

            <!-- Grid for Shlokas -->
            <div class="shloka-grid">
                <div class="shloka-card">
                    <h3>Shloka 1.1</h3>
                    <p>धर्मक्षेत्रे कुरुक्षेत्रे समवेता युयुत्सवः <br> मामकाः पाण्डवाश्चैव किमकुर्वत सञ्जय</p>
                </div>
                <div class="shloka-card">
                    <h3>Shloka 1.2</h3>
                    <p>दृष्ट्वा तु पाण्डवानीकं व्यूढं दुर्योधनस्तदा <br> आचार्यमुपसङ्गम्य राजा वचनमब्रवीत्</p>
                </div>
                <div class="shloka-card">
                    <h3>Shloka 1.1</h3>
                    <p>कर्मण्येवाधिकारस्ते मा फलेषु कदाचन। <br> मा कर्मफलहेतुर्भूर्मा ते सङ्गोऽस्त्वकर्मणि॥ (2.47)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="shloka-card">
                    <h3>Shloka 1.1</h3>
